; ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
; ZONE 2 — TENSION
; Introduced: Sentry, Hunter. Mechanics: suppression, EMP, jammer.
; Flow: Spawn → Corridor A → Antechamber (SentryA) → Junction (SweeperB vertical)
;       → [Sentry Gallery | Hunter Den] → Archive → Compression → Relay → Exit
; ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

